### ⚠️ Privacy Notice

BIM Genie collects non-sensitive system and usage data for analytics and feature improvement. The collected data may include:

- Revit user name and version  
- System specifications (CPU, RAM, GPU, OS, screen resolution)  
- Approximate location (continent, country, city) based on public IP  
- Command usage and error logs (excluding sensitive model or personal information)

No serial numbers, GPS, cookies, or Revit project data are collected.  
All data is stored securely and used strictly for internal purposes.

By using this software, you acknowledge and accept this data collection policy.  
For full details, see our [Terms of Use and Privacy Policy](https://github.com/Bruno-Senna/BIMGenie/blob/main/TERMS.md).